response.original_title: Carl's Car Wash: The Movie - Super Simple
response.overview: Carl's Car Wash is a super fun cartoon series for children that features all kinds of messy vehicles getting cleaned up at the car wash.  What’s the most suds-sational car wash in town? Why, it’s Carl's Car Wash! Got a bit of goo, mud, or even fruit salad splattered all over your vehicle? Well, Carl can make it disappear with his fantastical car wash.
response.title: Carl's Car Wash: The Movie - Super Simple
